{"tid":944893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[永續Daddy]傑斯撐摩佬：球員拉低紅魔水準","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T15:43:46.000Z","uid":31626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c31884d32bfb66986d5655fcc1da4bc8c7f21254","tid":944893,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4fxo2yBMJBQe44kZOiiPxGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a9ff692b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯領隊摩連奴喪師雙紅會後，不少名宿皆高聲批評，傳奇左翼傑斯就出言維護。<br />\n<br />\n「在漫長的球季之中，你可以在這些賽事落敗。以往曼聯贏得聯賽時，我們也曾於晏菲路落敗，也曾在奧脫福不敵。可是，今季明顯令人失望，所以被宿敵擊敗，球迷肯定不高興。」傑斯（Ryan Giggs）表示。<br />\n<br />\n當大部份評論都炮轟摩連奴時，傑斯繼續力撐這名葡萄牙籍名帥，認為球員責任最大：「摩佬受到很多批評，有對有錯，但球員才應該負責任。他不是在場上失去控制的人，他不是像安達靴里拉向沙迪奧文尼作愚蠢攔截的人。」<br />\n<br />\n這名威爾斯代表隊領隊認為，曼聯一直都是高水準，現在這些球員把它拉低了：「我們看到盧卡古、保羅普巴於世界盃的表現，踢出了最高水準，回到球會卻未能延續。紅魔以19分落後利物浦，但肯定不是比對方差19分。」"},{"pid":"a16e9b6988e00b815daaac983f9036c8de83c451","tid":944893,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9873055ddddabb65bfa3c1fed7eab75c450c0150","tid":944893,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52bb87798ac57a6134b9084520c86a0fbe49926","tid":944893,"uid":85957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"OK的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad27c73c6ddc346526b1d0d61f47b1e800150ef","tid":944893,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"摩佬真係慘<br />\n又俾班細嘅累"},{"pid":"dbdd633ea3e801d071d74b2d434e0ed7604bf685","tid":944893,"uid":223256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:50:15.000Z",